item.title: CVE-2023-5360|2024-08-02T07:59:44.302Z -- unknown -- royal%20elementor%20addons%20and%20templates
item.description: The Royal Elementor Addons and Templates WordPress plugin before 1.3.79 does not properly validate uploaded files, which could allow unauthenticated users to upload arbitrary files, such as PHP and achieve RCE.
